WEBVTT

00:10:29.720 --> 00:10:33.280
po aprontai su mortu.

00:10:34.520 --> 00:10:37.936
Nci ogaus praticas
chi cunfundint e atrupelliant

00:10:37.960 --> 00:10:41.440
e fadeus un sistema chi est bellu
e prenu de significau

00:10:42.320 --> 00:10:43.640
e trasluxenti.

00:10:45.080 --> 00:10:47.736
Nosus creeus ca su tratamentu
ecologicu de sa morti

00:10:47.760 --> 00:10:48.960
est unu diritu umanu.

00:10:52.640 --> 00:10:55.736
Ddu conosceis su diciu:

00:10:55.760 --> 00:10:59.226
chi podis torrai a compost una baca
podis torrai fintzas a unu cristianu?

00:10:59.226 --> 00:11:01.360
(Arrisu)